metadata.name: Gregor Split Second
metadata.description:
AI + Digital painting, 2022

Gregor was very relaxed until his agent opened the door.

Part of the collection “Curtain Caller” where I make portraits of artists minutes before they go on stage or perform.

This NFT was originally sold Aug 22, 2022, for 0.15 ETH on Evelyn O’s old Foundation.app profile
